            <h2>Features</h2>

            <h3>Framework</h3>

            <ul>
                <li>Routing exposed for extjs (integrated with <a href="https://github.com/FriendsOfSymfony/FOSJsRoutingBundle">FOSJsRoutingBundle</a>)</li>
