                <li>Ajax operations (integrated with <a href="https://github.com/hatimeria/HatimeriaExtJSBundle">HatimeriaExtJSBundle</a>)</li>
                <li>Powerful CRUD implementation</li>
                <li>One compiled javascript for production</li>
            </ul>

